text: As I’m watching #CNNTownHall tonight, I am so inspired by the audience - their stories, their courage, and their questions. I hope this event forever quells the misguided criticism that the millennial generation is politically apathetic. #FL07 #FlaPol #ParklandStudentsSpeak

THANK YOU @RepLanceNJ7 for becoming the third Republican to cosponsor my bill, #HR1478, to repeal the #DickeyAmendment and allow @CDCgov and other federal agencies to research gun violence. Let's get the facts we need to save lives. The momentum is promising. #FL07 #FlaPol

THIS JUST IN ---> I'm excited to announce @RosLehtinen is the newest Republican to cosponsor my bill, #HR1478, to repeal the #DickeyAmendment & allow the federal gov't to research gun violence. Thank you Ileana & @RepCurbelo for making this effort bipartisan #FL07 #FlaPol #sayfie

Yesterday, @SpeakerRyan said about the #ParklandShooting that “as public policymakers, we don’t just knee-jerk before we even have all of the facts and data.” Well then, Mr. Speaker, bring my bill to repeal #DickeyAmendment to a vote and let’s get the facts to stop this madness.

.@CDCgov should research gun violence, which is a public safety crisis. It's why last year I filed HR1478 to repeal #DickeyAmendment. Today, Trump appointee @SecAzar agreed with me. Congress should put people over politics & pass my bill to help save lives.

As a mom, my heart is broken at loss of life in #Parkland & I pray for all affected. As an American, I'm saddened another mass shooting plagues our nation. As a legislator, I'm frustrated by Congress’ inaction & motivated to keep working to stop senseless gun violence in America.

Heartbreaking what families at Marjory Stoneman Douglas High School in Parkland, Florida, are going through right now. We are all praying for them and our heroic law enforcement officials as they resolve this developing situation.
Shocked by the loss of Winter Springs Commissioner Pam Carroll, a dedicated public servant. My heart goes out to her family, friends, and everyone in the #WinterSprings community.

This morning, I spoke to seniors in #FL07 & listened to their concerns. This evening, I voted for a bill that would strengthen #SocialSecurity & ensure seniors get the benefits they've earned. HR 4547 would increase @SocialSecurity oversight, reduce fraud & protect beneficiary.

If we believe in family values in this country, then we must value families. I'm proud to support #PaidLeave. No parent in America should have to choose between caring for a newborn child and keeping a job to support his or her family. #FMLA25

On Holocaust Remembrance Day, #WeRemember the six million Jewish men, women, and children—and countless other innocent victims—killed by the Nazis. And we #NeverForget that the only thing necessary for evil to triumph is for good men and women to do nothing.

“Mom, there’s been a shooting” are  words that no parent should ever hear. My heart breaks for the victims of the #KentuckySchoolShooting and the families who will forever be affected by this tragic event. We must redouble our efforts to pass commonsense gun safety reforms.

Pleased that cooler heads prevailed & a deal has been reached. I intend to vote yes on new CR to allow good-faith bipartisan negotiations to continue & will urge my colleagues to do the same. Our goal should be a full-year budget that addresses our defense & domestic priorities.

Members of Congress shouldn't collect a salary while thousands of government employees are furloughed without pay. I’ll return my salary for every day the government is shut down because it's the right thing to do. #FlaPol

Members from both parties should not get paid if they cannot work together to pass a full-year budget that funds our military and critical domestic priorities. That is why I will return my salary every day that the government is shut down.

One year ago, we lost @OrlandoPolice Lt. Debra Clayton & @OrangeCoSheriff Deputy First Class Norman Lewis in the line of duty. On #LawEnforcementAppreciationDay, let's remember these two heroes & show our gratitude to all the brave  police officers who keep our communities safe.

Today marks 100 days since Congress allowed the Children’s Health Insurance Program to expire. We need to #RenewCHIP now before millions of children in Florida and other states lose their health care. My bipartisan bill to fund the program has 125 cosponsors. #FlaPol

Enabling law-abiding #TPS holders from El Salvador—including the 4,500 living in Florida—to remain in the U.S. is the right thing to do, morally and economically. I cosponsored a bipartisan bill authored by @RepCurbelo to provide them a pathway to legal status. #SaveTPS #FlaPol
What an amazing end to a PERFECT season. Congratulations to our home team, @UCF_Football, on becoming #PeachBowl champs! Couldn’t be prouder. #ChargeOn

NOTICIA: @USDOL otorgó $13 millones al estado de la Florida para proveer oportunidades de empleo a personas desplazadas por los huracanes Irma y María, en particular los ciudadanos estadounidenses de #PuertoRico y las Islas Vírgenes que se han reubicados a la FL por las tormentas

GOOD NEWS: @USDOL is awarding $13 million to the state of Florida to help provide job opportunities for individuals displaced by Hurricanes Irma & Maria, particularly American citizens from #PuertoRico & USVI who have relocated to FL in the wake of the devastating storms. #FlaPol

.@MCO has been directed to send 10 of its @CustomsBorder officers to the SW border in Jan., preventing these officers from performing their critical duties at the airport. I expressed my concerns to CBP & will meet w/senior officials to urge them to reverse this directive #FlaPol

A bipartisan coalition in the House voted to help FL, #PuertoRico, & other areas recover from recent disasters. I'm proud to have included robust funding in the bill for schools & colleges in states like Florida that are enrolling displaced students from Puerto Rico. #FlaPol
The only thing bipartisan about the GOP tax bill was its opposition.

Just voted against the GOP tax bill. Reform should simplify the tax code and empower middle-class families and small businesses to the greatest extent possible. This tax bill fails to achieve these objectives. Making matters worse: it adds over $1 trillion to our debt. #FlaPol

Congress failed to #ExtendCHIP by the deadline. Now the health care of millions of American children—including 375k children in FL and 50k in central FL—is in jeopardy. My bill to reauthorize #CHIP has +105 cosponsors. Congress must act to protect families.
Sending my thoughts to victims of the apparent terrorist attack in NYC and my thanks to the first responders who work tirelessly to keep our communities safe.

There are over 40,000 homeless veterans in America today. I’m pleased the VA reversed its decision to shift funding away from its highly-successful Supportive Housing initiative. No American—and especially no veteran—should have to live on the streets.

A healthy nation is a strong nation. I introduced a bill today that would:
 
-#ExtendCHIP, providing care for 400,000 children in Florida
-Reauthorize Community Health Centers, saving 160,000 American jobs
-Support states that provide care to displaced families from #PuertoRico

Congratulations to the 2017 @American_FB Conference champs, our UCF #Knights! This season of @UCF_Football has been nothing short of magical, and today's double overtime victory shows just how tough and talented this team is. On to a bowl game! #ChargeOn

Heart-stopping victory for @UCF_Football over valiant USF! Every player—from McKenzie Milton to Mike Hughes to Shaquem Griffin—gave a championship-worthy performance. @American_FB championship vs Memphis in Orlando next! #WarOnI4 #UCFvsUSF

Haitians living in the U.S. under #TPS have strengthened our economy & enriched our communities. Due to the Administration’s decision not to extend TPS for Haiti, I will cosponsor @RepCurbelo's bipartisan bill to allow these individuals to apply for legal permanent residence.

I voted against the #GOPTaxBill. When this process began, I said the bill needed to be bipartisan, help middle-class families and small businesses, and be fiscally responsible. Today's bill accomplishes none of those goals. #FlaPol
Pleased to announce that @USDOT has made a $15.3 million grant to @MyFDOT to repair or rebuild roads and highways damaged by Hurricane Irma.

Benefits of federal research:

⬆️ Auto safety ✅
⬇️ Highway casualties ✅
⬆️ Workplace safety ✅

But because of Dickey Amdt:

⬆️ Gun safety ❌
Victims of gun violence deserve elected leaders who are willing to enact basic reforms that respect the 2nd Amdt & prevent future tragedies.
My heart goes out to Sutherland Springs & all the families impacted by this horrific act. Grateful to our brave first responders.
Wishing 15th-ranked, undefeated @UCF_Football good luck tonight against SMU. Go Knights! #RiseandConquer
Disappointed GOP decided to take partisan path to tax reform. We must work together to make improvements that help small biz & middle class.
While I'm still reviewing new GOP tax plan, I'm pleased @RepKevinYoder & I helped rescue child care tax credit. Still pushing for expansion.
My thoughts are w/victims of Manhattan attack & the NYPD officers who responded w/courage. America won’t bend or break in the face of evil.
Good news! @strongnationUSA has endorsed the #PACEAct, my bill with @RepKevinYoder to make child care more affordable. #FlaPol
A bipartisan group of lawmakers & I met w/WH officials yesterday to discuss the need for investments in our nation’s infrastructure. #FlaPol
The VA should provide the highest-quality care to our veterans. Today I voted to protect whistleblowers & prevent wrongdoing in the agency.
I just voted for a disaster relief package that will help Florida, Puerto Rico, USVI and Texas recover from devastating hurricanes. #FlaPol

As #YomKippur begins, I wish my Jewish friends in central Florida and around the world spiritual fulfillment and a meaningful fast.
Joined new #PuertoRico Economic Development & Prosperity Caucus w/@RepJenniffer to push hurricane relief & equality for our fellow Americans
Fellow Americans in #PuertoRico & #USVI need more resources now. U.S. must swiftly address the logistical challenges delaying aid delivery.
Dreamers are an integral part of the fabric of America. Proud to sign the petition to force a vote on a clean #DREAMAct. #ProtectDreamers
Heartbroken by loss of life & devastation in PR. I'll stand w/Gov. @ricardorossello & @RepJenniffer to support recovery in Congress.
L'Shana Tova to all my Jewish friends. Have a happy and blessed new year! #RoshHashanah
Spoke to PR Gov @ricardorossello about #Maria & assured him I'll work to get PR the support it needs. We're all part of the American family.
Pleased to announce @SFB_Airport has received a $5.6 million @FAANews grant to support its expansion project. Great news for C. Florida!
I'm monitoring Hurricane Maria & thinking about our fellow Americans in Puerto Rico & USVI, as well as our other friends in the Caribbean.
Each day, 20 veterans commit suicide. They fought for us. Now we must fight for them here at home. #BeThere #SuicidePreventionWeek
My thoughts are with the Florida Keys and everyone in the path of #HurricaneIrma. Stay safe, Florida.
To search for open shelters, text SHELTER & your zip code to 43362 (4FEMA). For example: SHELTER 32789. #HurricaneIrma #FL07
(1/2) Just had productive call w/White House Homeland Security Advisor @TomBossert45 on #HurricaneIrma prep & recovery for central Fla.
Everyone should prepare NOW for #HurricaneIrma. Leaders at all levels are taking this storm very seriously. You & your family should as well
If anyone in central Florida has issues with a federal agency during/after #HurricaneIrma, please call my office toll free at 1-888-205-5421
I’ll work with congressional leadership and the White House to ensure we get what we need, when we need it. #HurricaneIrma
My office is coordinating with @DHSgov @fema & @RedCross to ensure resources get on the ground quickly after the storm. #HurricaneIrma
As a member of Armed Services Committee, I'm working w/Armed Forces & VA to ensure we take care of service members, veterans & mil families.
As a Member of Congress, I’m focused on ensuring government works together at all levels – local, state, and federal. #HurricaneIrma
Time is running out, but there is still time to prepare for #HurricaneIrma. We should all hope for the best, but prepare for the worst.
This is a serious, life-threatening situation for us. Please take the warnings & directions from local officials seriously. #HurricaneIrma
There is no doubt or guessing: #HurricaneIrma is a very large and powerful hurricane heading straight for central Florida. Prepare now.
Thanks all who are helping us prepare for & respond to #Irma - esp @FLGuard, law enforcement & first responders. We are #OrlandoStrong.
I'm at Orlando Emergency Operations Center to join @orlandomayor & others for briefing on #HurricaneIrma preparations. Press conf at 1:30pm.
Just spoke to @citybeautiful @orlandomayor Buddy Dyer offering my full support to prepare for & respond to #HurricaneIrma. #FL07
On #LaborDay we honor all that the labor movement has done to strengthen America's working families. I'm proud to fight alongside you.
Today was just a"taste" of many great locally-owned food options in Sanford - we'll do more later! What's your favorite?? #SanfordFoodTour
To promote downtown #Sanford's growing food scene & its small businesses, I stopped by a few places today for a mini #SanfordFoodTour! #FL07
The U.S. is filled w/ officers who fight crime AND respect the Constitution. Sheriff Arpaio abused his power & shouldn't have been pardoned.
Women won the right to vote 97 years ago & have kept fighting for progress ever since. Much work remains to be done. #WomensEqualityDay
Keeping Texas in my thoughts tonight and praying for the safety of all those affected by Hurricane Harvey. #Harvey2017
A #TransgenderBan deprives our military of thousands of qualified personnel & hurts those who simply seek to serve & defend our nation.
Heartbroken by loss of USS John S. McCain sailors. We must take swift steps to ensure no more American lives are lost to incidents like this
To help the Afghan govt defeat the Taliban, US & NATO must use smart & strategic military force paired with robust, US-led diplomacy. (1/2)
My heart breaks over the loss of @kissimmeepolice officer Baxter & for the attacks against our officers here, in Jacksonville & Fairchance.
Those who advise the president hold incredible influence over the fate of all Americans. Their views cannot be toxic & dangerous. (1/3)
Deeply disturbed by POTUS's comments. Leaders set the tone. We must be unequivocal against racism, xenophobia & antisemitism.
Social Security is not an entitlement; it's a benefit earned after a lifetime of hard work. Keep the promise. #SocSec82
There's no place for such hate & violence in our society. Our country needs unity now. The events at #Charlottesville are shameful.
The so-called #SkinnyRepeal means a $734 annual premium hike for Floridians. We're moving in the wrong direction here. #FlaPol #FL07
We have always honored sacrifice & patriotism. Banning transgender Americans from serving violates those values. To ALL who serve: thank you
Senate might have voted to advance the #ACA repeal, but the fight is far from over. Your voices are needed more than ever. #ProtectOurCare
The veterans, seniors, students & working families who make #FL07 such a vibrant community are my #MondayMotivation. Ready to work for them!
.@SenJohnMcCain is the epitome of toughness & grit. My thoughts & best wishes are with this true American hero & his family.
Can't put politics over people & expect to win. The #HealthcareBill failed thnx to calls, emails, stories & actions of Americans everywhere.
Political gestures don't make for good #healthcare policy. Our system needs bipartisan fixes, not the rug pulled out from under it.

Proud to stand with @LGBTEqCaucus in fighting for ALL of our servicemembers by defeating the #HartzlerAmd. Equality wins! #NDAA18 #FlaPol
Like the original, the revised Senate health care bill was crafted in secret & still leaves families, seniors & veterans worse off. #FlaPol
Political parties don't define us. #NationalDayofCivility is about finding common ground with our neighbors through civility & respect.
Saddened by the barbaric act of violence against #AmarnathYatra pilgrims. People everywhere must stand united against hate.
New emails showing Russia ties to Trump campaign are disturbing & contradict past denials. Special Counsel & Congress must get to the facts.
‼️#CBOSCORE is in‼️Senate #HealthCareBill leaves 22M uninsured & will ⬆️ premiums ⬇️ benefits for millions more. Especially bad for Florida.
#TitleIX has protected students from sex based discrimination for 45 years. Let's make sure schools remain a place of safe learning for all.
This #HealthcareBill was crafted behind closed doors without bipartisan input or a single public hearing. The American people deserve better
Heartbroken by passing of Otto Warmbier. His memory must strengthen our resolve to address the cruel human rights violations of North Korea.
Our hearts and thoughts are with the Sailors and their families affected by the USS Fitzgerald collision. Praying they find the missing.
On my way to House floor to join colleagues in praying for recovery of Rep @SteveScalise, @CapitolPolice & all affected by today's shooting.
My thoughts are with Rep. Scalise & all those injured in the ballpark shooting - including heroic @capitolpolice officers.
Today's testimony by #JamesComey was an important step in restoring the public's trust in our democratic institutions & electoral processes.
My heart breaks for those affected by today's shooting in #Orlando. Praying for speedy recovery of injured & for families of those killed.
As always, the #Orlando community is grateful for speed, bravery & professionalism of first responders, especially @OrangeCoSheriff's office
Addressing climate change & promoting clean, renewable energy benefits Fla. & the economy. Leaving the #ParisAgreement hurts those efforts.
Ramadan Mubarak to my Muslim friends observing the holy month. I wish you & your family a spiritually rejuvenating fast & a blessed Ramadan.
#CBOSCORE confirms what we already knew: #TrumpCare is a bad deal that would raise premiums & cut benefits for millions of Americans #FlaPol
The President's budget is morally & fiscally irresponsible. We need a bipartisan budget that sets families on a path to prosperity. #FlaPol
My heart breaks for all those families affected by the Manchester bombing, and is filled with gratitude for the brave first responders.
1/2 Appointment of special counsel for #RussiaInvestigation is a positive step toward uncovering the truth. We must #FollowTheFacts. #FlaPol
If other nations can't trust us to keep shared classified info secret, then they will stop sharing it with us - making us less safe. #FlaPol
Following #Comey firing, we need swift, independent investigation into Russian influence in 2016 election & ties to the White House. #FlaPol
Congrats to all who are graduating this weekend! Be proud of your accomplishment & be sure to thank those who helped. Best of luck! #FL07
#TrumpCare was negotiated behind closed doors, did not receive single public hearing & has no @USCBO score. This is a BAD DEAL #FL07 #FlaPol
#TrumpCare: millions lose coverage; people w/pre-existing conditions at risk; ⬆️premiums; ⬇️benefits. I oppose & will vote NO. #FL07 #FlaPol
(1/2) Today I voted to keep the gov't open through the rest of the fiscal year & fund many key central Florida priorities...  #FL07 #FlaPol
Happy #SmallBusinessWeek! Thank you to the 2.3 million small businesses in FL that strengthen our economy & create more than 3M jobs. #FL07
Every person deserves access to clean air, water and land; it's also key to strengthening our state's economy. #FL07 #EnvironmentalJustice
I will not vote for a health care bill that takes away life-saving protections for Americans with pre-existing conditions. #FL07 #TrumpCare
On #HolocaustRemembranceDay, we mourn the millions of Jews & others who died & honor the survivors. We also vow: #NeverAgain. #FL07 #FlaPol
Protecting Florida's natural resources will strengthen our economy & preserve our state's beauty for generations to come. #EarthDay #FL07
